Squizzy::

She was very groggy. She opened her eyes and saw she was being caried 
by a bot. She recognized his face but coudn't remember his name. She 
leaned her head back and closed her eyes again.  She felt dizzy and 
wasn't sure what was wrong. She had a pain in her shoulder where the 
needle had stuck her. She groanes softly and looked up at Havoc. Her 
vision was a little blurry. She leaned her head against his shoulder 
and tried to run a self diognostic.  She felt the system run.  It 
showed that she had a chemical in her body. And it was the chemical 
that made her feel so out of it. She whispered, "What happened?"
